From Saturday (April 18), you can only satisfy your @mcdsg craving during the circuit breaker period through the fast food chain’s delivery system, GrabFood or “drive-thru” outlets.
McDonald's said that all of its restaurants here will temporarily remove takeaways until May 4 as an added safety precaution.
